msgstr "**Retirez les trous dont la surface est inférieure à**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1764
msgid "``MIN_AREA``"
msgstr "``MIN_AREA``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1768
msgid ""
"Only holes with an area less than this threshold will be deleted. With a "
"value of ``0.0``, **all** the holes will be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Seuls les trous d'une superficie inférieure à ce seuil seront supprimés. "
"Avec une valeur de ``0.0``, **tous** les trous seront supprimés."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1771
