msgstr "``REMOVE_EMPTY``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5453
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5498
msgid "**Non null geometries**"
msgstr "**Géométries non nulles**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5468
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5494
msgid "**Null geometries**"
msgstr "**Géométries nulles**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5471
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5495
msgid "``NULL_OUTPUT``"
msgstr "``NULL_OUTPUT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5474
msgid "Default: ``[Skip output]``"
msgstr "Par défaut : ``[Ignorer la sortie]``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5497
msgid "Output vector layer (for NULL and, if chosen, empty geometries)"
msgstr ""
"Couche vecteur de sortie (pour les géométries NULL et, si elles sont "
"choisies, vides)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5501
msgid ""
"The output vector layer (without NULL and, if chosen, empty geometries)"
msgstr ""
"La couche de vecteurs de sortie (sans NULL et, si elle est choisie, des "
"géométries vides)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5506
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:removenullgeometries``"
msgstr "**ID de l'algorithme** : ``native:removenullgeometries``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5516
msgid "Reverse line direction"
msgstr "Inverser la direction de la ligne"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5517
msgid "Inverts the direction of a line layer."
msgstr "Inverse la direction d'une couche de ligne."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5522
msgid "Before and after the direction inversion"
msgstr "Avant et après l'inversion de direction"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5543
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5567
msgid "**Reversed**"
msgstr "**Renversé**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5570
msgid "The output line vector layer (with reversed lines)"
msgstr "La couche de vecteur de ligne de sortie (avec des lignes inversées)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5575
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:reverselinedirection``"
msgstr "**ID de l'algorithme** : ``native:reverselinedirection``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5585
msgid "Rotate"
msgstr "Rotation"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5586
msgid ""
"Rotates feature geometries by the specified angle clockwise. The rotation "
"occurs around each feature's centroid, or optionally around a unique preset "
"point."
msgstr ""
"Fait pivoter les géométries d'entités de l'angle spécifié dans le sens "
"horaire. La rotation se produit autour du centre de gravité de chaque "
"entité, ou éventuellement autour d'un point prédéfini unique."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5594
msgid ":ref:`qgistranslategeometry`, :ref:`qgisswapxy`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgistranslategeometry`, :ref:`qgisswapxy`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5612
msgid "**Rotation (degrees clockwise)**"
msgstr "**Rotation (degrés dans le sens horaire)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5617
msgid "Angle of the rotation in degrees"
msgstr "Angle de rotation en degrés"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5618
