msgstr "[coordonnées]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5625
msgid ""
"X,Y coordinates of the point to rotate the features around. If not set the "
"rotation occurs around each feature's centroid."
msgstr ""
"Coordonnées X, Y du point pour faire pivoter les entités autour. S'il n'est "
"pas défini, la rotation se produit autour du centre de gravité de chaque "
"entité."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5629
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5653
msgid "**Rotated**"
msgstr "**Pivoté**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5656
msgid "The output vector layer with rotated geometries"
msgstr "La couche vectorielle de sortie avec des géométries pivotées"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5661
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:rotatefeatures``"
msgstr "**ID de l'algorithme** : ``native:rotatefeatures``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5671
msgid "Roundness"
msgstr "Rondeur"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5702
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5726
msgid "**Roundness**"
msgstr "**Rondeur**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5734
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:roundness``"
msgstr "**ID de l'algorithme**: ``native:roundness``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5744
msgid "Segmentize by maximum angle"
msgstr "Segmentation par angle maximum"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5745
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5823
msgid ""
"Segmentizes a geometry by converting curved sections to linear sections."
msgstr ""
"Segmente une géométrie en convertissant des sections courbes en sections "
"linéaires."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5748
msgid ""
"The segmentization is performed by specifying the maximum allowed radius "
"angle between vertices on the straightened geometry (e.g the angle of the "
"arc created from the original arc center to consecutive output vertices on "
"the linearized geometry). Non-curved geometries will be retained without "
"change."
msgstr ""
"La segmentation est effectuée en spécifiant l'angle de rayon maximal "
"autorisé entre les vertex sur la géométrie redressée (par exemple l'angle de"
" l'arc créé à partir du centre de l'arc d'origine vers les vertex de sortie "
"consécutifs sur la géométrie linéarisée). Les géométries non courbes seront "
"conservées sans changement."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5754
msgid ""
":ref:`qgissegmentizebymaxdistance`, :ref:`qgissimplifygeometries`, "
":ref:`qgissmoothgeometry`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgissegmentizebymaxdistance`, :ref:`qgissimplifygeometries`, "
":ref:`qgissmoothgeometry`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5773
msgid "**Maximum angle between vertices (degrees)**"
msgstr "**Angle maximum entre les vertex (degrés)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5777
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7208
msgid "Default: 5.0"
msgstr "Par défaut : 5.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5778
msgid ""
"Maximum allowed radius angle between vertices on the straightened geometry"
msgstr ""
"Angle de rayon maximal autorisé entre les vertex de la géométrie redressée"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5780
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5804
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5858
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5882
